  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Hilton Garden Inn is offered on a half board basis with breakfast and dinner included with your stay. </p>
<p>Breakfast and dinner are taken in the hotel's onsite Garden Grille &amp; Bar Restaurant.</p>
<p>Breakfast includes a continental buffet with hot and cold options, with a 'cooked to order' for eggs and omelettes.</p>
<p>Dinner is a 3 course evening meal with a choice of main course, serving local traditional dishes.</p>
<p>You will also find drinks and snacks available in the 24-hour Pavilion Pantry.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
