  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Hilton Garden Inn is an attractive 4 star hotel located in Davos. </p>
<h2>Easy transport links</h2>
<p>This hotel is in a really convenient location in Davos, about 5 minutes walk to Davos Platz and the Jakobshorn cable car. It's also next to the Horlauben bus station where you'll find buses that will take you straight to the ski area. There's plenty for you to explore during your holiday in the Swiss Alps.</p>
<h2>Fantastic service </h2>
<p>You'll be in for a comfortable stay thanks to the hotel's friendly staff and the amenities on offer. Throughout your holiday, you'll have access to a range of spa facilities including a sauna and steam room - which are perfect for relaxing the muscles in preparation for another day on the slopes. If you'd like to keep active off of the mountain, the hotel also has a fitness centre that you can use.</p>
<h2>Bar and lounge area </h2>
<p>After dinner, we recommend stopping at the bar area for a drink or two before bed. You can either have a seat at the bar, or you can relax in the hotels communal lounge area, featuring comfy sofas and a cosy fireplace.</p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
