  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Hilton Garden Inn is located 5 minutes from Davos Platz, and offers a range of facilities throughout your stay. Visit the sauna and steam room for some well needed relaxation hours, or maintain your stamina in the fitness room. The bus stop is located just outside the hotel, where you'll find buses taking you to the slopes and ski lifts. This hotel is offered on a half board basis, with breakfast and dinner served in the onsite Grille &amp; Bar Restaurant. </p>]]></listingDescription>
